CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1969, pg. 17 reads: "Recently Wed - Mr. and Mrs. Walter Scott Jr., were recently married by the Rev. Eugene Roberts of First Baptist Church, Penn Hills. The bride is the former Ida Mae Edwards, daughter of Mrs. Evalina Edwards.  The groom is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Charles Walter Scott."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of groom Walter Scott Jr. and bride Ida Mae Edwards Scott wearing sleeveless empire waist dress with lace panels, cutting three tiered wedding cake, posed in interior with peacock decoration, Penn Hills
